description: Set the MessageFeedbackStatus as RECEIVED or FAILED for the passed in MessageId. If you use message feedback then you must update message feedback record. When you receive a signal that a user has received the message you must use PutMessageFeedback to set the message feedback record as RECEIVED; Otherwise, an hour after the message feedback record is set to FAILED.

parameters.name: MessageId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the message.

parameters.name: MessageFeedbackStatus
parameters.description: Set the message feedback to be either RECEIVED or FAILED.

nested_items.name: MessageId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the message.

nested_items.name: MessageFeedbackStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the message.
